  "texts": [
    "Details of those models and associated applications are highlighted below.",
    "48, author proposed an adaptive threshold module (ATM) for An SNN based architecture.",
    "ATM algorithm controls internal threshold potential.",
    "This ATM is used to control output firing rate, which helps to to extract the information encoded in input stimulus.",
    "The model is validated on speech TIDIGITS and RWCP data-sets."
  ]
}